>[Question]
>I want help in converting kg to Lbs.  My friend in Poland said she 
>weighs 120 kg.  I want to order her an American shirt and I don't 
>know what size.  How many lbs in 120 kg.
>Thanks Loads

   The conversion is 1 pound = 0.453 kg

so  120 kg =  120/0.453 = 264.9 pounds

                      say  265 pounds

